ExcelFunctions.ExcelToMiddle(classNum, placement)¶

This function overwrites the middle.txt file with the updated array

Args:

classNum (str): eg. “1” placement (str): eg. “database”, “middle”

Returns:

middle<classNum>.txt have new data from excel

ExcelFunctions.MiddletoExcel(classNum, placement)¶

This function overwrites middle<classNum>.txt file and student names to excel to create a table

Args:

classNum (str): eg. “1” placement (str): eg. “database”, “middle”

Returns:

excel spreadsheet is filled with studnet names and true/false data display name to row 1 and colA (reade classes2-<#>.txt)
